VT Autologin:
sudo systemctl edit getty@tty1
add following lines:
[Service]
ExecStart=
ExecStart=-/usr/bin/agetty --autologin username --noclear %I $TERM

rEFInd manual boot entries:
add: scanfor manual, external

menuentry Arch {
	icon Path/to/Icon
	loader vmlinuz-linux
	initrd initramfs-linux.img
	options "rw root=UUID=... quiet initrd=intel-ucode.img initrd=initramfs-linux.img"
}

menuentry Win {
	icon Path/to/icon
	loader path/to/loader/bootmgfw.efi
}

NetworkManger disable autocreation of resolv.conf:
change dns=none in /etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.conf

fstab automount drives:
UUID=... /path/to/mountpoint ntfs-3g(or whatever fs) nofail,auto,noatime,rw 0 0
